{"tid":632060,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android手機Mon報銷，想救資料","createTime":"2018-04-17T05:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T11:49:52.000Z","uid":129393,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4ced8e770393a6cdbda97402fd451e27c68901","tid":632060,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"小米3爆芒，嚴重Ghost touch/ touch detect唔到（解到鎖但基本上做唔到任何操作）；將會買新Android機<br />\n<br />\n冇開USB debugging（即係mirror唔到個touch screen上電腦做操作），駁落電腦亦detect唔到storage只能叉電（應該冇開相關USB設定）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>只想救返whatsapp紀綠</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中平時有用Google Drive backup，但唔記得左interval幾耐、幾時last backup（有冇得喺GDrive介面應check？）<br />\n<br />\n請問大神點解可以救返whatsapp紀綠？<br />\n<br />\n個人猜想，如果有間整機舖可以幫個靚忙，幫我駁個spare Mon、應該就可以即時做一次Google Drive backup、應該就可以喺新機無縫拎返紀綠（唔知我咁樣理解有冇錯？）如果得，大家知唔知邊間整機鋪有得咁樣？我已打算今晚落先達問，但怕個個都用「救資料」名目收得好貴，但其實我只係想禁多下backup就夠..."},{"pid":"f65c09dcfbb8591ab8f3824926a04adc28490fe7","tid":632060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"usb otg線駁mouse"},{"pid":"395cd8a447750281435852f8f44b00b680f185b1","tid":632060,"uid":11660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"睇到畫面？連usb mouse 撳lo"},{"pid":"687b339a2f1455a18ed132184eedb0abe6ab3fb3","tid":632060,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f65c09dcfbb8591ab8f3824926a04adc28490fe7","tid":632060,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"usb otg線駁mouse"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"多謝大神，唔知有得咁玩，即試！"},{"pid":"c8c503ba1bba906efb700e48572a1498611f761c","tid":632060,"uid":129393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"多謝大神，用OTG-&gt;mouse方法已成功備份wtsapp<br />\n<br />\n而家希望試埋可唔可以access埋手機啲fil